    "Out of the total 250 keywords, only 246 met the selected threshold criteria.",
    "This resulted in 3 clusters, 16 co-occurrence items with 96 common links, and a total strength of 250, as shown in Fig. 4.",
    "The size of each node represents the frequency of term co-occurrence (i.e., how often they appear together as keywords).",
    "The thickness of the relationship indicates the frequency of keyword co-occurrence.",
    "The connections represent the interconnection between two items, and the node strength reflects the significance of that particular item."
